		{
			"type": "text",
			"version": 162,
			"versionNonce": 400869352,
			"isDeleted": false,
			"id": "SIz1qyHS",
			"fillStyle": "solid",
			"strokeWidth": 2,
			"strokeStyle": "solid",
			"roughness": 1,
			"opacity": 100,
			"angle": 0,
			"x": 949.1223217460803,
			"y": 1191.0746398548454,
			"strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
			"backgroundColor": "transparent",
			"width": 1156.319091796875,
			"height": 100,
			"seed": 1637634712,
			"groupIds": [],
			"frameId": null,
			"roundness": null,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1778864052847,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"text": "• Open addressing: if bucket occupied, probe other indices (linear / quadratic / double hashing) until empty slot found.\n• Dynamic resizing + rehashing when load factor (items / buckets) grows — spreads keys out again.\n\nBoth chaining and open addressing aim for “few keys per bucket” on average.",
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "• Open addressing: if bucket occupied, probe other indices (linear / quadratic / double hashing) until empty slot found.\n• Dynamic resizing + rehashing when load factor (items / buckets) grows — spreads keys out again.\n\nBoth chaining and open addressing aim for “few keys per bucket” on average.",
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"baseline": 61,
			"index": "b1D",
			"autoResize": true,
			"hasTextLink": false,
			"rawText": "• Open addressing: if bucket occupied, probe other indices (linear / quadratic / double hashing) until empty slot found.\n• Dynamic resizing + rehashing when load factor (items / buckets) grows — spreads keys out again.\n\nBoth chaining and open addressing aim for “few keys per bucket” on average."
		}
